Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.50,0:01:09.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  闹钟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.50,0:01:09.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good morning, alarm clock
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.31,0:01:22.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到底要选哪个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.31,0:01:22.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Choices, choices
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.86,0:01:31.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤子穿反了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.86,0:01:31.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pants are a little twisted around
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.08,0:01:52.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,差点忘了我的幸运领带夹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.08,0:01:52.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Almost forgot my lucky tie clip
Dialogue: 1,0:01:58.38,0:02:00.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.38,0:02:00.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.57,0:02:14.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小姐  让我来帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.57,0:02:14.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Young lady, allow me
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.15,0:02:17.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.15,0:02:17.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, you
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.12,0:02:24.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.12,0:02:24.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Morning, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.87,0:02:26.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  下水道修理工
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.87,0:02:26.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Sewer Man
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.95,0:02:29.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好个幸运儿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.95,0:02:29.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There goes one lucky boy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.96,0:02:33.84,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(628,336)}停
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.67,0:02:32.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明天见  小可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.67,0:02:32.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow, sweetie
Dialogue: 1,0:02:36.05,0:02:37.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.05,0:02:37.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whoopsie
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.48,0:02:52.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.48,0:02:52.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.86,0:02:56.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你今天一大早怎么精力这么旺盛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.86,0:02:56.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And why are you so peppy this morning?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.57,0:03:00.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为今天是我的幸运日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.57,0:03:00.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Because today is my lucky day
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.24,0:03:02.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都是我幸运领带夹的功劳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.24,0:03:02.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,thanks to my lucky tie clip
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.37,0:03:06.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你领带夹不是天天都戴着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:06.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you wear that tie clip every day?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.99,0:03:09.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,每天都是我的幸运日
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.99,0:03:09.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Every day is my lucky day
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.92,0:03:14.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才没运气这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.92,0:03:14.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Luck isn't real
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.42,0:03:15.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都是你在脑袋里乱想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.42,0:03:15.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's all in your head
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.88,0:03:20.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  不相信运气会倒大霉的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.88,0:03:20.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, it's unlucky not to believe in luck
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.01,0:03:23.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.01,0:03:23.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Mr. Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.30,0:03:24.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没看到你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.30,0:03:24.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Didn't see you there
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.12,0:03:50.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一份豪华腌椰菜蟹黄堡  完美特制
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:50.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One Krabby Patty pickle deluxe, perfectly prepared
Dialogue: 1,0:03:52.42,0:03:55.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我倒要锐评一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.42,0:03:55.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll be the judge of that
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.72,0:04:06.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我很想投诉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.72,0:04:06.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want to complain
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.47,0:04:10.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但也太好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:10.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But it's too delectable
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.18,0:04:12.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.18,0:04:12.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.73,0:04:16.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么做到这么完美的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.73,0:04:16.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How did you accomplish such perfection?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.90,0:04:18.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该是我运气好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:18.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Guess I'm just lucky
Dialogue: 1,0:04:40.59,0:04:42.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,第二天早上
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.89,0:04:50.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好再过一个幸运日了吗  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.89,0:04:50.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready to start another lucky day, Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.15,0:05:07.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的幸运领带夹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.15,0:05:07.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's my lucky tie clip?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:07.57,0:05:08.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不在这
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.57,0:05:08.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not here
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.41,0:05:10.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.41,0:05:10.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.58,0:05:11.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.58,0:05:11.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nuh-uh
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.84,0:05:22.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.84,0:05:22.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.59,0:05:29.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的幸运领带夹不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.59,0:05:29.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My lucky tie clip is missing
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.43,0:05:35.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.43,0:05:35.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh no
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.14,0:05:36.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上班要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.14,0:05:36.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm late for work
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.48,0:05:37.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等会再找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.48,0:05:37.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll search for it later
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.74,0:05:54.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.74,0:05:54.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:05:54.54,0:05:56.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我今天来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.54,0:05:56.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was running late today
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.87,0:05:58.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  太倒霉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.87,0:05:58.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jeez, what bad luck
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.88,0:06:01.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,交出钱包
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.88,0:06:01.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me your wallet
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.46,0:06:02.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,动作快
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.46,0:06:02.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Make it snappy
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.01,0:06:07.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明天见  小可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.01,0:06:07.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow, sweetie
Dialogue: 1,0:06:11.72,0:06:13.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.72,0:06:13.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whoopsie
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.35,0:06:14.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,热狗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.35,0:06:14.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hot dog
Dialogue: 1,0:06:14.39,0:06:15.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来买热
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.39,0:06:15.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get your hot--
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.95,0:06:29.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.95,0:06:29.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What happened to you?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.91,0:06:32.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我幸运领带夹丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.91,0:06:32.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I lost my lucky tie clip
Dialogue: 1,0:06:32.28,0:06:34.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在所有事都出了错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.28,0:06:34.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and now everything is going wrong
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.24,0:06:37.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,根本就没运气这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.24,0:06:37.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's no such thing as luck
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.37,0:06:40.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的破领带夹跟这玩意一点关系都没
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.37,0:06:40.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your dumb tie clip has nothing to do with it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.50,0:06:43.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥又可怜又天真
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:43.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Poor naive Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.72,0:06:56.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,锅铲抽筋了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.72,0:06:56.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spatula cramp
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:05.73,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(680,300)}此处点餐
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.57,0:07:08.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请问有没有什么推荐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.57,0:07:08.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you have any recommendations?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.90,0:07:09.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.90,0:07:09.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.70,0:07:11.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去别家吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.70,0:07:11.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eat somewhere else
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.70,0:07:14.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,建议得十分绝妙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.70,0:07:14.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excellent advice
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.28,0:07:16.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢  小伙子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.28,0:07:16.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, young man
Dialogue: 1,0:07:16.33,0:07:17.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小费
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.33,0:07:17.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A tip?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.66,0:07:19.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天一定是我幸运日
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.66,0:07:19.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Must be my lucky day
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.91,0:07:21.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,并不是说我信了那套胡话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.91,0:07:21.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not that I believe in that nonsense
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.71,0:07:28.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一份蟹黄堡套餐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.71,0:07:28.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One Krabby Patty combo
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.26,0:07:39.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,汽水没气了  薯条太油了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.26,0:07:39.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The soda is flat, the fries are oily
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.89,0:07:44.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且蟹黄堡没味道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.89,0:07:44.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and the Krabby Patty is bland
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.23,0:07:47.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没味道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.23,0:07:47.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,B-b-b-bland?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.24,0:07:52.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是怎么了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.24,0:07:52.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's the matter with you, boyo?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.61,0:07:55.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我倒大霉了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.61,0:07:55.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm bad luck, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.07,0:07:56.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,倒霉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.07,0:07:56.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bad luck
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.33,0:07:58.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,倒霉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.33,0:07:58.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bad luck?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.58,0:08:00.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王的生意好坏全靠运气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.58,0:08:00.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The restaurant business runs on luck
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.91,0:08:06.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,倒霉一来  蟹堡王就要完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.91,0:08:06.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If bad luck sets in, the Krusty Krab is doomed
Dialogue: 1,0:08:06.46,0:08:07.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都出去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.46,0:08:07.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everyone out
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.29,0:08:08.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出去出去出去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.29,0:08:08.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Out, out, out, out, out
Dialogue: 1,0:08:08.46,0:08:10.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得烧点干海草
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.46,0:08:10.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got to burn some dried kelp
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.21,0:08:12.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把这里的坏运气全净化了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.21,0:08:12.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and cleanse this joint of any bad mojo
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.26,0:08:15.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.26,0:08:15.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.18,0:08:15.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:15.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.89,0:08:16.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们今天放假
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.89,0:08:16.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take the day off
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.89,0:08:18.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放假
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.89,0:08:18.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Day off?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.81,0:08:21.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.81,0:08:21.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.64,0:08:22.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.64,0:08:22.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.94,0:08:27.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但愿我的好运气
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.94,0:08:27.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hope my good luck
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.36,0:08:29.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,转移到了有需要的人身上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:29.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,went to someone who needed it
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.07,0:08:34.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一根头发
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:34.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A hair?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:35.11,0:08:38.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝的好运气多半转到我身上了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.11,0:08:38.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'm getting SpongeBob's good luck
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.71,0:08:44.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.71,0:08:44.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.17,0:08:45.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.17,0:08:45.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:08:45.75,0:08:46.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.75,0:08:46.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You OK?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:47.79,0:08:50.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我幸运领带夹丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.79,0:08:50.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I lost my lucky tie clip
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.50,0:08:54.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在我全天下最倒霉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.50,0:08:54.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am now the unluckiest person alive
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.63,0:08:56.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能不能来抱一个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:56.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I have a hug?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:56.55,0:08:58.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.55,0:08:58.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.35,0:09:01.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,无论如何我都不碰你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.35,0:09:01.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't touch you with a 10-foot pole
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.35,0:09:01.77,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(790,920)}十 尺 长 杆
Dialogue: 1,0:09:01.77,0:09:05.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可不能让你的霉运传染给我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.77,0:09:05.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't want your bad luck to rub off on me
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.60,0:09:08.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.60,0:09:08.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What am I going to do?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.73,0:09:12.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然你就再找个护身符吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.73,0:09:12.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why don't you find a new lucky charm?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.15,0:09:15.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好办法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.15,0:09:15.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great idea
Dialogue: 1,0:09:15.70,0:09:16.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.70,0:09:16.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.37,0:09:20.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没你我都不知道该怎么办了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.37,0:09:20.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know what I'd do without you
Dialogue: 1,0:09:20.45,0:09:23.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的幸运十一尺长杆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.45,0:09:23.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,my lucky 11-foot pole
Dialogue: 1,0:09:26.58,0:09:28.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,幸运  幸运
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.58,0:09:28.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lucky, lucky
Dialogue: 1,0:09:29.63,0:09:30.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,四叶海草
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.63,0:09:30.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A four-leaf kelp
Dialogue: 1,0:09:31.21,0:09:33.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这种东西可幸运了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.21,0:09:33.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're really lucky
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.93,0:09:41.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,新建了条公路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.93,0:09:41.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A new freeway?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.68,0:09:43.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就不幸运了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.68,0:09:43.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's not lucky
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.90,0:09:49.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一只海兔脚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.90,0:09:49.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A sea bunny's foot
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.77,0:09:51.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,更幸运了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.77,0:09:51.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're extra lucky
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.73,0:09:58.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,除非脚还长在海兔子身上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.73,0:09:58.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Unless it's still attached to the sea bunny
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.91,0:10:00.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.91,0:10:00.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:10:15.21,0:10:16.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.21,0:10:16.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:25.06,0:10:28.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,某些人运气好得不得了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.06,0:10:28.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Some people have all the luck, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.39,0:10:30.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,反正好的不是你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.39,0:10:30.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just not you
Dialogue: 1,0:10:43.70,0:10:45.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的领带夹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.70,0:10:45.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My tie clip?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:45.49,0:10:48.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原来我整天都带着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.49,0:10:48.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I had it with me all day?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:49.12,0:10:50.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就跟章鱼哥说的一个样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:50.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It was just like Squidward said
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.25,0:10:53.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.25,0:10:53.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward, you were right
Dialogue: 1,0:10:53.50,0:10:55.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,运气都在我脑袋里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.50,0:10:55.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Luck was all just in my head
Dialogue: 1,0:10:55.42,0:10:58.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个纯金领带夹再也用不上了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.42,0:10:58.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't need this solid gold lucky tie clip
Dialogue: 1,0:11:02.39,0:11:05.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过保险一点也无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.39,0:11:05.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But it never hurts to be on the safe side
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.52,0:11:17.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  我的好运气回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.52,0:11:17.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward, my good luck is back
Dialogue: 1,0:11:17.44,0:11:18.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回到我脑袋里了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.44,0:11:18.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Back in my head
Dialogue: 1,0:11:19.86,0:11:20.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.86,0:11:20.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold on
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.86,0:11:24.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果海绵宝宝的运气回来了  那
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.86,0:11:24.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If SpongeBob's luck is back, then--
Dialogue: 1,0:11:32.08,0:11:33.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.08,0:11:33.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:11:43.59,0:11:45.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真倒霉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.59,0:11:45.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just my luck
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.68,0:11:50.27,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H00FFB5&}睡魔降临
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.43,0:11:51.69,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(700,350)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.43,0:11:51.69,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(684,656)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.43,0:11:56.11,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1530,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.89,0:11:53.19,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(688,580)}指导总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.35,0:11:54.65,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(726,542)}统筹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.81,0:11:56.11,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(558,546)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.27,0:11:57.73,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(656,544)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.27,0:11:57.73,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1468.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.82,0:11:58.73,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1110,562)}水母田
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.37,0:12:08.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你来捉  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.37,0:12:08.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got him, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:12:08.66,0:12:11.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要被我捉到了  水母
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.66,0:12:11.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're mine now, jelly
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.93,0:12:25.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,一觉之后
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.22,0:12:31.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我睡了多久
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.22,0:12:31.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How long was I out?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.89,0:12:35.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大概一星期
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.89,0:12:35.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,About a week
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.52,0:12:38.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,破纪录了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.52,0:12:38.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A new record
Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.77,0:12:41.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  熟能生巧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.77,0:12:41.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's all in the old wrist
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.58,0:12:53.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,睡一整天最能消耗精力了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.58,0:12:53.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing like a day of napping to tucker you out
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.12,0:12:55.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚安  台灯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.12,0:12:55.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good night, Mr. Lamp
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.34,0:13:01.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.34,0:13:01.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not sleeping yet
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.76,0:13:03.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,换这个姿势躺试试
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.76,0:13:03.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe if I lay this way
Dialogue: 1,0:13:12.56,0:13:16.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还是坐等变困好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.56,0:13:16.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll just sit up and wait to get sleepy
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.73,0:13:20.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,连续24小时睡不着之后
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.07,0:13:26.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,已经等睡着等了一整天了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:26.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting to sleep all day
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.99,0:13:29.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,时间早都到斑点半了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.99,0:13:29.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's already half past a freckle
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.95,0:13:32.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是看看海绵宝宝在干嘛好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.95,0:13:32.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Guess I'll see what SpongeBob's doing
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.04,0:13:40.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要来玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.04,0:13:40.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Want to hang out?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.55,0:13:43.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.55,0:13:43.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, it's you
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.05,0:13:44.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这么晚来干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.05,0:13:44.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here so late?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.92,0:13:46.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.92,0:13:46.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't sleep
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.22,0:13:47.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来做事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.22,0:13:47.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's do stuff
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.72,0:13:49.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.72,0:13:49.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK, sure
Dialogue: 1,0:13:49.89,0:13:53.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我四小时后就必须要起床
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.89,0:13:53.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I have to be up in four hours
Dialogue: 1,0:13:53.72,0:13:54.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.72,0:13:54.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perfect
Dialogue: 1,0:14:00.77,0:14:02.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你居然要打赢我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.77,0:14:02.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you're beating me
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.74,0:14:11.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你又赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.74,0:14:11.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You win again?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.41,0:14:12.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.41,0:14:12.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right
Dialogue: 1,0:14:13.12,0:14:15.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三百局两百胜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.12,0:14:15.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Best 200 out of 300
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.04,0:14:23.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁第一个挖到石头滩  谁就赢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.04,0:14:23.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,First one to dig to rock bottom wins
Dialogue: 1,0:14:38.02,0:14:40.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  虽然好玩归好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.02,0:14:40.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, this is really fun and all
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.31,0:14:41.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我真得睡觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.31,0:14:41.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I need to get to bed
Dialogue: 1,0:14:42.11,0:14:44.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我还是睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.11,0:14:44.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I still can't sleep
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.78,0:14:48.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你一定得快点去睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.78,0:14:48.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, you've got to get some sleep and fast
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.49,0:14:51.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然会出幻觉的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.49,0:14:51.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or else you could start seeing things
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.62,0:14:52.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.62,0:14:52.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.32,0:14:54.87,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1058,920)}看见东西
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.32,0:14:54.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在就出幻觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.32,0:14:54.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm seeing things now
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.33,0:14:55.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,房子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.33,0:14:55.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,House
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.29,0:14:57.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,地面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.29,0:14:57.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ground
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.08,0:14:58.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天空
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.08,0:14:58.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sky
Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.25,0:15:00.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快让幻觉停下来  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.25,0:15:00.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Make it stop, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.46,0:15:02.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.46,0:15:02.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Make it stop
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.13,0:15:05.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.13,0:15:05.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, pal
Dialogue: 1,0:15:05.63,0:15:06.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.63,0:15:06.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll help you get to--
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.38,0:15:10.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我睡觉才对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.38,0:15:10.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's my sleep
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.18,0:15:14.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,睡着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.18,0:15:14.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sleep
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.31,0:15:21.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就只需要盖好被子  喝点热牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.31,0:15:21.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All you need is a good tucking in and some warm milk
Dialogue: 1,0:15:28.57,0:15:30.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再来点菊花茶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.57,0:15:30.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And some chamomile tea
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.78,0:15:36.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听我最爱的催眠曲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.78,0:15:36.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And my favorite lullaby
Dialogue: 1,0:15:57.10,0:16:00.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  我还是睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.10,0:16:00.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, I still can't sleep
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.40,0:16:07.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来只能用传统办法解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.40,0:16:07.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like I'll have to do this the old-fashioned way
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.87,0:16:18.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还很清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.87,0:16:18.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm still awake
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.88,0:16:26.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是很清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.88,0:16:26.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Still awake
Dialogue: 1,0:16:35.72,0:16:38.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好像能行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.72,0:16:38.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think it's working
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.06,0:16:41.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.06,0:16:41.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.19,0:16:48.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万不得已也只能动杀手锏了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.19,0:16:48.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to do this, but I'm down to my last resort
Dialogue: 1,0:16:55.78,0:16:57.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.78,0:16:57.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:16:57.16,0:16:58.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.16,0:16:58.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.37,0:17:01.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你三更半夜来干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.37,0:17:01.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what could you possibly want at this hour of the night?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:03.29,0:17:06.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要听你的生平事迹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.29,0:17:06.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need to hear your life story
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.33,0:17:08.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,果然是要来犯傻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.33,0:17:08.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought, an idiotic--
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.63,0:17:09.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.63,0:17:09.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:09.50,0:17:12.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要听我的生平事迹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.50,0:17:12.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You need to hear my life story?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.76,0:17:13.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.76,0:17:13.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yep
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.72,0:17:18.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这么突然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.72,0:17:18.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, it's such short notice
Dialogue: 1,0:17:18.26,0:17:21.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我完全没准备啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.26,0:17:21.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't have anything prepared
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.43,0:17:24.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就只准备了这本草稿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.43,0:17:24.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,except this rough manuscript
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.94,0:17:30.27,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(654,570)}章鱼哥\N八条腿八条命\N第一卷
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.31,0:17:26.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,名叫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.31,0:17:26.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I call it
Dialogue: 1,0:17:26.31,0:17:30.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  八条腿八条命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.31,0:17:30.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Tentacles: Eight Legs, Eight Lives"
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.36,0:17:35.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可你只有四条腿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.36,0:17:35.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But you only have four legs
Dialogue: 1,0:17:35.78,0:17:37.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还外加俩胳膊咧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.78,0:17:37.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And two arms
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.70,0:17:39.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.70,0:17:39.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:17:39.12,0:17:40.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加起来就八条了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.12,0:17:40.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that makes eight
Dialogue: 1,0:17:41.41,0:17:42.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第一章
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.41,0:17:42.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Chapter 1
Dialogue: 1,0:17:42.49,0:17:45.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我年纪轻轻就才华横溢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.49,0:17:45.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"In my youth, my brilliance was evident
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.46,0:17:48.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那时我并没有浪费时间交朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.46,0:17:48.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Instead of wasting my time making friends
Dialogue: 1,0:17:48.17,0:17:49.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而是创作艺术
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.17,0:17:49.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I made art
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.96,0:17:53.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还记得自己画了幅复杂爪绘图
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.96,0:17:51.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"I recall making
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.00,0:17:53.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a rather sophisticated tentacle painting
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.80,0:17:54.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就连我的老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.80,0:17:54.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that even my teacher--"
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.88,0:17:55.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.88,0:17:55.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute
Dialogue: 1,0:17:55.97,0:17:57.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一点都没困
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.97,0:17:57.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not getting sleepy
Dialogue: 1,0:17:57.63,0:17:59.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只觉得无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.63,0:17:59.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm just getting bored
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.68,0:18:00.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一片茫然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.68,0:18:00.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"--and perplexity
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.80,0:18:04.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,眼睁睁看着我因成就而得奖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.80,0:18:04.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,as I was bequeathed an award for my achievements"
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.52,0:18:09.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,起码我的水管能让他睡着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.52,0:18:09.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, at least my pipe works for him
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.03,0:18:15.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是没法变困
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.03,0:18:15.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I'm not sleepy
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.28,0:18:18.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就得累坏自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.28,0:18:18.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll just have to tire myself out
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.91,0:18:21.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有热狗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.91,0:18:21.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A hot dog
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.08,0:18:23.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.08,0:18:23.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me
Dialogue: 1,0:18:27.66,0:18:29.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,几天后
Dialogue: 1,0:18:32.84,0:18:34.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.84,0:18:34.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.55,0:18:42.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抓到了  你这小老头
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.55,0:18:42.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got you now, you little old man
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.39,0:18:47.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要看我孙子孙女的照片吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.39,0:18:47.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You want to see a picture of my grandkids?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:53.11,0:18:54.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.11,0:18:54.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.78,0:18:56.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是睡不着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.78,0:18:56.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Still not sleeping, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.28,0:18:59.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么看出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.28,0:18:59.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How can you tell?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:59.91,0:19:00.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,直觉而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.91,0:19:00.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just a hunch
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.41,0:19:04.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来得让睡魔来看看你才行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.41,0:19:04.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like you need a visit from the Sandman
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.41,0:19:06.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他会朝你眼睛吹睡眠沙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.41,0:19:06.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He'd blow a little sand in your eyes
Dialogue: 1,0:19:06.70,0:19:08.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后你就能一下子睡过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.70,0:19:08.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and you'd be out like a light
Dialogue: 1,0:19:09.16,0:19:11.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,睡魔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.16,0:19:11.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A Sandman
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.08,0:19:14.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,眼睛  一下子睡过去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.08,0:19:14.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eyes, out like a light
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.01,0:19:20.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.01,0:19:20.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.84,0:19:22.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.84,0:19:22.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you later
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.39,0:19:29.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来做个睡魔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.39,0:19:29.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me make Sandman
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.44,0:19:38.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  睡魔先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.44,0:19:38.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK, Mr. Sandman
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.94,0:19:42.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快朝我眼睛吹睡眠沙  让我睡着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.94,0:19:42.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now blow sand in my eyes and put me to sleep
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.33,0:19:46.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.33,0:19:46.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.24,0:19:47.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还要沙子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.24,0:19:47.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You need more sand?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.50,0:19:58.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我回来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.50,0:19:58.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get back here
Dialogue: 1,0:19:58.67,0:20:00.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先抓到我再说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.67,0:20:00.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll have to catch me first
Dialogue: 1,0:20:12.94,0:20:15.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,酷啊  有个疯子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.94,0:20:15.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cool, a raving lunatic
Dialogue: 1,0:20:15.31,0:20:19.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要把你追到天涯海角  睡魔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.31,0:20:19.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll chase you to the ends of the ocean, Sandman
Dialogue: 1,0:20:27.87,0:20:29.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终于啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.87,0:20:29.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Finally
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.33,0:20:32.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就对了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.33,0:20:32.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.08,0:20:33.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多来点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.08,0:20:33.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Keep it coming
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.17,0:20:39.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.17,0:20:39.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:40.26,0:20:42.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还没困呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.26,0:20:42.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not sleepy yet
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.14,0:20:51.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.14,0:20:51.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.98,0:20:52.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.98,0:20:52.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,More
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.77,0:20:56.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.77,0:20:56.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.20,0:21:03.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好点了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.20,0:21:03.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Better
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.40,0:21:05.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我还要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.40,0:21:05.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I need more
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.59,0:21:23.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,睡魔  你的破烂睡眠沙一点用都没
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.59,0:21:23.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandman, your stupid sleep sand doesn't work
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.34,0:21:24.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.34,0:21:24.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, stop
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.67,0:21:26.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那不是睡魔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.67,0:21:26.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's no Sandman
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.34,0:21:28.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.34,0:21:28.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:21:37.15,0:21:40.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回忆录又要加一条不幸遭遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.15,0:21:40.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Another misadventure for my memoir
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.86,0:21:42.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一点用都没有  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.86,0:21:42.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's no use, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.73,0:21:46.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么睡魔睡眠沙完全没法让我变困
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.73,0:21:46.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All the Sandman's sand couldn't make me sleepy
Dialogue: 1,0:21:50.03,0:21:55.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这后半辈子只好一直清醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.03,0:21:55.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll just be awake for the rest of my life
Dialogue: 1,0:21:58.46,0:22:00.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果说你要永远清醒下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.46,0:22:00.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you're going to be awake forever
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.75,0:22:03.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就可以好好利用一下  从中受益
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.75,0:22:03.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,then you might as well put that to good use
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.97,0:22:08.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  还真是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.97,0:22:08.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, you were right
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.64,0:22:11.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可以一直醒着  正好就能
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.64,0:22:11.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My "awakeyness" makes me the perfect
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.81,0:22:15.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,通宵当个长途卡船司机了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.81,0:22:15.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,all-night long-haul trucker
Dialogue: 1,0:22:17.31,0:22:19.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,收到  好兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.31,0:22:19.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,10-4, good buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.15,0:22:21.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  请安全驾驶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.15,0:22:21.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, keep your rubber side down
Dialogue: 1,0:22:21.61,0:22:23.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把挡风玻璃的虫子清理掉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.61,0:22:23.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and the bugs off your glass
Dialogue: 1,0:22:23.48,0:22:24.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们等会再见
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.48,0:22:24.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll catch you on the flip
